安装cryptopp库
1.从github下载：https://github.com/weidai11/cryptopp
2.编译安装：
    make
    make test
    sudo make install

Linkable-Ring-Signature环签名项目编译运行
1.下载：https://github.com/apuljain/Linkable-Ring-Signature
2.在include目录中的CommonFunctions.hpp中增加#include <cassert>
3.进入src目录执行：
g++ CommonFunctions.cpp LinkableRingSignProver.cpp LinkableRingSignVerifier.cpp main.cpp -I ../include -lcryptopp
  
./a.out
